---
title: Smoked Ham & Cheese Sliders 2x the delicious portions!
description: This big batch of warm, toasty sliders features sesame buns layered with smoky ham and chopped pickles, plus both cheddar and Monterey Jack cheeses for the ultimate melty combo. Tangy sesame mustard butter coats the golden-brown sliders, which get served with roasted potato wedges and a crisp lettuce-cabbage salad tossed in an irresistible garlicky vinaigrette.
